      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SPRING MILES (1) hit the frame latest (30.23) when second at this track in a Grade 5. Has six wins already from this draw. Expected to be in the finish. ZIPPING FIYERO (7) is a capable type and proved too strong last time to win by 2.25 lengths at Sandown in a handy 29.67 beating Upended. Solid formlines coming through his last run. Likely to be in the finish. PAW DAMON (6) has been in the money at his last two runs, most recently when third beaten 1.5 lengths (29.90). Has a win and two places times at this track. Although beaten ran one of the quickest times on the card last start. Can feature again. POINT BREAK (4) is last start winner who looks one of the chances.",
